CorelCAD 2014.0 build 13.8.12 (x64)

CorelCAD 2014 offers industry-standard CAD features , tools, three-dimensional and two-dimensional high-precision design and enhanced support files dwg. The ability to open , edit, and distribute files in dwg format simplifies working with colleagues and suppliers . Customizable two-dimensional and three-dimensional design exactly help turn ideas into drawings and models. A full set of industry standard features, including the Ribbon interface and enhanced tools layers allow start work immediately . New " Design Resources " provide access to design tools and the ability to reuse them . CorelCAD works on Windows and Mac OS with the same high speed and performance, and offers a variety of customizable options and support graphics CorelDRAW.
